<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-surface">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 font-display">Built in the open</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        OwnPulse is licensed under AGPL-3.0. Anyone can read the code, audit the data handling, and run
        their own instance. Any company that offers OwnPulse as a hosted service must publish their
        modifications — improvements flow back to the community.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        The data export schema is CC0 — public domain. Any application can read an OwnPulse export
        without license obligation. Your data is never locked in a proprietary format.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        Governance is cooperative. Members elect board seats. Architecture decisions are public.
        This is infrastructure that serves its users, not its investors.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ownpulse/ownpulse"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border-2 border-neutral-300 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:border-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors"
      >
        GitHub repository
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ownpulse/ownpulse/blob/main/schema/open-schema.json"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border-2 border-neutral-300 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:border-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors"
      >
        Open data schema
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ownpulse/ownpulse/blob/main/docs/guides/self-hosting.md"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border-2 border-neutral-300 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:border-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors"
      >
        Self-hosting guide
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
